data.text:
Frank Castillo

Frank Castillo has worked his way up at the iconic Los Angeles venue, The World Famous Comedy Store where he is now a Paid Regular. Frank became a staple of The Comedy Store Roast Battles, and in January of 2017, Frank became the Champion of Roast Battle II on Comedy Central, he’s been on Showtime and he Roasted Mr. Peanut in a Super Bowl Commercial, Frank will be headlining his own show during the Netflix is a Joke Festival.
